data.description: Fantastic community upgrades are starting in 2024 including: New elevators, exterior building/window sealing, cosmetic updates, possible pool resurfacing and more! With an engaged and proactive HOA, it's a great time to buy at 100 Park. Seller will pay 2024 Reserve Projects Assessment (estimated to be $20,000) at closing. Welcome to your urban oasis in the heart of Uptown Denver! This stunning 2nd-floor condo in a high-rise building offers the perfect blend of modern luxury and convenience. With 780 square feet of space, this home features one spacious bedroom with an en-suite full bath and two closets, providing ample storage. Enjoy breathtaking sunrise views that create a serene atmosphere to start your day. The large living room is ideal for entertaining, and an additional bonus room serves as a perfect home office or extra living space. The kitchen is equipped with granite counters and stainless appliances. Panoramic windows frame the view, adding a scenic backdrop to your daily routine. Convenience is key with underground parking, ensuring your vehicle is both secure and easily accessible. The building's amenities include a gym for staying active, a seasonal pool and hot tub for relaxation, and even a dedicated dog park for your furry friend. Situated in Uptown Denver, this condo is surrounded by an array of fun restaurants, parks, and popular Colorado sights, including Coors Field and the Denver Zoo. This is not just a home; it's a lifestyle. Immerse yourself in the vibrant energy of Uptown Denver and schedule your showing today to experience the best of urban living in the Mile High City!
